div class=\"ffb-id-48iibgd4 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"fg-vcenter-wrapper\"><div class=\"fg-vcenter\"><div class=\"fg-match-column-inside-wrapper\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-48iibgd8 fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">GI\u1ea2I TH\u01af\u1edeNG &amp; CH\u1ee8NG NH\u1eacN<\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-48iibgd9 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Doanh Nghi\u1ec7p Xanh 2024<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Th&agrave;nh Ph\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Vi\u1ec7t Nam-gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Travel + Leisure Luxury Awards Asia Pacific 2024<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Travelers' Choice Award 2024 - Top 10% kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u1edfi Tripadvisor<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Th&agrave;nh Ph\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Vi\u1ec7t Nam - DestinAsian Reader's Choice Awards 2024<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull;&nbsp; Ti&ecirc;u chu\u1ea9n Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Xanh ASEAN - C\u1ee5c Du L\u1ecbch Qu\u1ed1c Gia Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n 5 sao h&agrave;ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2023 - trao b\u1edfi S\u1edf Du l\u1ecbch Th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch&iacute; Minh<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Top 5 Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n uy t&iacute;n t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2023<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 Earth Check h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea1ch kim 2023<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Doanh nghi\u1ec7p Xanh TP.HCM 2023<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Th&agrave;nh Ph\u1ed1 sang tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t ch&acirc;u &Aacute;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Top 10 Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 T\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Travel+Leisure Ch&acirc;u &Aacute; Th&aacute;i B&igrave;nh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 2023<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Top 10% kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr&ecirc;n Tripadvisor<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Top 100 Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n &amp; Khu ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng Th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 2022 d&agrave;nh cho kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle Saigon<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Top 100 T\u1ed5ng Qu\u1ea3n L&yacute; Xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 2022 d&agrave;nh cho T\u1ed5ng Qu\u1ea3n L&yacute; c\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i &ndash; &Ocirc;ng Jean Philippe Lovotti<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Top 10 Kh&aacute;ch S\u1ea1n &amp; Resorts T\u1ed1t Nh\u1ea5t Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2020 do \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a t\u1ea1p ch&iacute; du l\u1ecbch danh ti\u1ebfng DestinAsian b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Ch\u1ea5t L\u01b0\u1ee3ng D\u1ecbch V\u1ee5 Xu\u1ea5t S\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Tripadvisor t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2011 \u0111\u1ebfn 2020<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110&aacute;nh Gi&aacute; C\u1ee7a Kh&aacute;ch H&agrave;ng b\u1edfi Agoda n\u0103m 2018, 2019, 2020<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Kh&aacute;ch S\u1ea1n Xanh T\u1ed1t Nh\u1ea5t Vi\u1ec7t Nam trao t\u1eb7ng b\u1edfi Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i Th\u01b0\u01a1ng M\u1ea1i Ch&acirc;u &Acirc;u 2019<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Kh&aacute;ch S\u1ea1n Xanh Khu V\u1ef1c \u0110&ocirc;ng Nam &Aacute; giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2016 &ndash; 2018<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn EarthCheck c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 V&agrave;ng t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2015 \u0111\u1ebfn 2019<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; &Aacute; Qu&acirc;n Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n d&agrave;nh cho Doanh Nh&acirc;n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf S&agrave;i G&ograve;n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao \u0111\u1ed5i T\u1ea1p ch&iacute; Business Traveller Khu V\u1ef1c Ch&acirc;u &Aacute; Th&aacute;i B&igrave;nh D\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u0103m 2015<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; &Aacute; Qu&acirc;n Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Kinh Doanh B\u1ec1n V\u1eefng c\u1ee7a Hi\u1ec7p H\u1ed9i Th\u01b0\u01a1ng M\u1ea1i &Uacute;c n\u0103m 2018<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng M&ocirc;i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam trao t\u1eb7ng b\u1edfi B\u1ed9 T&agrave;i Nguy&ecirc;n &amp; M&ocirc;i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u0103m 2015<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Ch\u1ea5t L\u01b0\u1ee3ng D\u1ecbch V\u1ee5 Xu\u1ea5t S\u1eafc c\u1ee7a GoHotels.com n\u0103m 2018<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng &ldquo;40 n\u0103m c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho ng&agrave;nh du l\u1ecbch Th&agrave;nh Ph\u1ed1&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao t\u1eb7ng b\u1edfi S\u1edf Du l\u1ecbch Th&agrave;nh Ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch&iacute; Minh<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Top 10 kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n 5 sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch nh\u1ea5t trao t\u1eb7ng b\u1edfi S\u1edf Du L\u1ecbch Th&agrave;nh Ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch&iacute; Minh t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2013 \u0111\u1ebfn 2016<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110&aacute;nh Gi&aacute; C\u1ee7a Kh&aacute;ch H&agrave;ng b\u1edfi TripAdvisor &laquo;Best of the Best&raquo; 2013 &amp; 2014<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-48iibgd3{ padding-top: 50px;padding-right: 50px;padding-bottom: 50px;padding-left: 50px;}.ffb-id-48iibgd9 ,.ffb-id-48iibgd9:before,.ffb-id-48iibgd9:after,.ffb-id-48iibgd9 *,.ffb-id-48iibgd9 *:before,.ffb-id-48iibgd9 *:after{ color: #490042 !important;}.ffb-id-48iibgd9{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-48iibgd9:before,.ffb-id-48iibgd9:after,.f