om b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn &ndash; 2011.<\/p>\n<p>- The Guide Awards 2011 &ndash; &ldquo;N\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ph&aacute;t tri\u1ec3n l&acirc;u \u0111\u1eddi, s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng, v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ed1n c&oacute; v&agrave; l&agrave; kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n c&oacute; v\u1ecb tr&iacute; \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i trung t&acirc;m S&agrave;i G&ograve;n&rdquo;.<\/p>\n<p>- Top 3 Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n h&agrave;ng \u0111\u1ea7u Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp v&agrave;o danh s&aacute;ch Top 20 Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n c&oacute; ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h&agrave;ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, t\u1ea1p ch&iacute; Travel + Leisure b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn &ndash; 2011.<\/p>\n<p>- \"Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n \u0111&aacute;p \u1ee9ng s\u1ef1 mong \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng\" - Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Du L\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Rakuten 2010.<\/p>\n<p>- Top 4 Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n h&agrave;ng \u0111\u1ea7u Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp v&agrave;o danh s&aacute;ch 500 Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n h&agrave;ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, t\u1ea1p ch&iacute; Travel + Leisure b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn &ndash; 2010.<\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh&aacute;ch doanh nh&acirc;n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t - 2009, 2010&rdquo;, Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i Du L\u1ecbch c&aacute;c kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n trao t\u1eb7ng<\/p>\n<p>- Top 3 &ldquo;Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh&aacute;ch doanh nh&acirc;n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Tp. HCM &ndash; 2010&rdquo;, B\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc t\u1ea1p ch&iacute; Business Traveller b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn - T\u1ea1p ch&iacute; du l\u1ecbch n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Ch&acirc;u &Aacute; Th&aacute;i B&igrave;nh D\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/p>\n<p>- The Guide Awards 2010 - &ldquo;Ph&aacute;t tri\u1ec3n du l\u1ecbch b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng &amp; B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 M&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng&rdquo;.<\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Xanh ASEAN 2010 - 2011&rdquo;, Hi\u1ec7p H\u1ed9i Du L\u1ecbch Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; Ban Th\u01b0 K&yacute; Hi\u1ec7p H\u1ed9i c&aacute;c n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110&ocirc;ng Nam &Aacute; trao t\u1eb7ng n\u0103m 2010.<\/p>\n<p>- B\u1eb1ng Khen c\u1ee7a \u1ee6y Ban Nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n trao t\u1eb7ng Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle l&agrave; \u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb ch\u1ea5p h&agrave;nh t\u1ed1t v\u1ec1 Ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch Thu\u1ebf n\u0103m 2009.<\/p>\n<p>- Saigon Times Top 40 Awards trao t\u1eb7ng Kh&aacute;ch S\u1ea1n Caravelle l&agrave; doanh nghi\u1ec7p c&oacute; v\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo&agrave;i kinh doanh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2009 v&agrave; t&ocirc;n vinh c&aacute;c gi&aacute; tr\u1ecb Xanh c\u1ee7a kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n. <\/p>\n<p>- Saigon Saigon Bar - Top 10 \u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u1ea3i tr&iacute; th&uacute; v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1, trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh &ldquo;TPHCM 100 \u0110i\u1ec1u th&uacute; v\u1ecb&rdquo;, S\u1edf V\u0103n H&oacute;a Th\u1ec3 Thao &amp; Du L\u1ecbch trao t\u1eb7ng.<\/p>\n<p>- Gi\u1ea3i Nh&igrave; cu\u1ed9c thi &ldquo;T&ograve;a Nh&agrave; hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 IV 2009&rdquo;<\/p>\n<p>- Vi\u1ec7t Nam Golden FDI l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2009 trao t\u1eb7ng Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 thu\u1ebf n\u0103m 2008<\/p>\n<p>- B\u1eb1ng khen c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee7 t\u01b0\u1edbng Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n D\u0169ng trao t\u1eb7ng Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng th&agrave;nh t&iacute;ch trong c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 thu h&uacute;t \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo&agrave;i v&agrave; tham gia \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 t\u1ea1i th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch&iacute; Minh v&agrave; c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n<p>- B\u1eb1ng khen c\u1ee7a Ch\u1ee7 T\u1ecbch \u1ee6y Ban Nh&acirc;n D&acirc;n Th&agrave;nh Ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch&iacute; Minh - &ocirc;ng L&ecirc; Ho&agrave;ng Qu&acirc;n trao t\u1eb7ng Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle \u0111&atilde; t&iacute;ch c\u1ef1c tham gia \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v&agrave; \u0111\u1ea1t th&agrave;nh t&iacute;ch xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t kinh doanh, \u0111&oacute;ng g&oacute;p trong c&aacute;c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m li&ecirc;n t\u1ee5c, g&oacute;p ph\u1ea7n l&agrave;m t\u0103ng ng&acirc;n s&aacute;ch thu\u1ebf c\u1ee7a th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1, nh&acirc;n k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m 20 n\u0103m thu h&uacute;t \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo&agrave;i tr&ecirc;n \u0111\u1ecba b&agrave;n th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 (th&aacute;ng 6 n\u0103m 2009)<\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch s\u1eed th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1, n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c ngon v&agrave; c&aacute;c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n &acirc;m nh\u1ea1c \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc&rdquo; do t\u1ea1p ch&iacute; The Guide trao t\u1eb7ng n\u0103m 2009<\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;Top 40 doanh nghi\u1ec7p kinh doanh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3&rdquo; do t\u1ea1p ch&iacute; uy t&iacute;n Saigon Times b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn n\u0103m 2008<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-48iibq71 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-el-has-bg fg-text-dark\"><span class=\"fg-bg\"><span data-fg-bg=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;color&quot;,&quot;opacity&quot;:1,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;#ffffff&quot;}\" class=\"fg-bg-layer fg-bg-type-color \" style=\"opacity: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\"><\/span><\/span><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-48iibq74 fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/ASEAN-Green-Hotel-Award-2016-2018-1.jpg\" alt=\"ASEAN-Green-Hotel-Award-2016-2018\"><div class=\"ffb-id-48iibq75 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;Gi\u1eef v\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr&iacute; trung t&acirc;m c\u1ee7a S&agrave;i G&ograve;n, Caravelle ng&agrave;y nay v\u1eabn duy tr&igrave; c&aacute;c ti&ecirc;u chu\u1ea9n v&agrave;ng trong su\u1ed1t 10 n\u0103m qua. Phong c&aacute;ch qu\u1ea3n l&yacute; chu\u1ea9n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. C&oacute; th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c.&rdquo; do t\u1ea1p ch&iacute; The Guide trao t\u1eb7ng n\u0103m 2008<\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Vi\u1ec7t Nam&rdquo; n\u0103m 2007 do Hi\u1ec7p H\u1ed9i Du L\u1ecbch Vi\u1ec7t Nam trao t\u1eb7ng n\u0103m 2008<\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Xanh c\u1ee7a \u0110&ocirc;ng Nam &Aacute; - 2008&rdquo; do Ban Th\u01b0 K&yacute; Hi\u1ec7p H\u1ed9i c&aacute;c n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110&ocirc;ng Nam &Aacute; trao t\u1eb7ng <\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n c&oacute; v\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo&agrave;i kinh doanh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t&rdquo;, S&agrave;i G&ograve;n Times trao t\u1eb7ng trong n\u0103m 2004 v&agrave; 2007<\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n \u0111&aacute;p \u1ee9ng m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 mong \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a kh&aacute;ch&rdquo;, t\u1ea1p ch&iacute; the Guide b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn 2006-2007<\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t&rdquo;, \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 Vietnamnet b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn.<\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n sang tr\u1ecdng &ndash; ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng&rdquo; do Seven Stars v&agrave; Stripes b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn.<\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;10 kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch nh\u1ea5t - 2006&rdquo;, b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc b&aacute;o S&agrave;i G&ograve;n Gi\u1ea3i Ph&oacute;ng b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn.<\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;100 Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n sang tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi - 2006&rdquo;, b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc t\u1ea1p ch&iacute; Robb Report b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn.<\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;10 kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n h&agrave;ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam - 2005, 2006&rdquo;, Hi\u1ec7p H\u1ed9i Du L\u1ecbch Vi\u1ec7t Nam b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn<\/p>\n<p>- B\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc T\u1ea1p Ch&iacute; DestinAsia b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn &ldquo;Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch&iacute; Minh&rdquo; n\u0103m 2005<\/p>\n<p>- B\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc T\u1ea1p Ch&iacute; Business Traveller, t\u1ea1p ch&iacute; du l\u1ecbch n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Ch&acirc;u &Aacute; Th&aacute;i B&igrave;nh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v&agrave; th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn &ldquo;Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t d&agrave;nh cho doanh nh&acirc;n t\u1ea1i Th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch&iacute; Minh&rdquo; 4 n\u0103m li\u1ec1n 2002-2005<\/p>\n<p>- B\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc T\u1ea1p Ch&iacute; The Guide b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn &ldquo;Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n sang tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch&iacute; Minh&rdquo; 6 n\u0103m li\u1ec1n (2005, 2004, 2003, 2002, 2001 &amp; 1999)<\/p>\n<p>- Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng do t\u1ea1p ch&iacute; Entr&eacute;e E, t\u1ea1p ch&iacute; cao c\u1ea5p chuy&ecirc;n vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c du l\u1ecbch, c&ocirc;ng nh\u1eadn kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle l&agrave; &ldquo;m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao t\u1eb7ng b\u1edfi &ocirc;ng William Tomicki, bi&ecirc;n t\u1eadp vi&ecirc;n v&agrave; l&agrave; ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n t\u1ea1p ch&iacute; <br \/>Entr&eacute;e E.<\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n h&agrave;ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t&rdquo; do Asia Travel Tips.com b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn<\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau 2 n\u0103m kinh doanh 2002 &amp; 2004&rdquo; do Asiahotels.com b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn<\/p>\n<p>- Saigon Saigon Bar&nbsp; - &ldquo;Bar t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch&iacute; Minh&rdquo; n\u0103m 2003, t\u1ea1p ch&iacute; The Guide - 2003<\/p>\n<p>- &ldquo;Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khu v\u1ef1c Ch&acirc;u &Aacute;&rdquo; do Hi\u1ec7p H\u1ed9i Kh&aacute;ch S\u1ea1n Th\u1ebf Gi\u1edbi (WORLDHOTELS) b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><style>.ffb-id-48iibgd3{ \npadding-top: 50px;\npadding-right: 50px;\npadding-bottom: 50px;\npadding-left: 50px;\n\n}\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9 ,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9:before,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9:after,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9 *,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9 *:before,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9 *:after{ \ncolor: #490042 !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9{ \nfont-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9:before,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9:after,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9:hover,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9:focus,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9 *,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9 *:before,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9 *:after,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9 *:hover,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9 *:focus{ \nfont-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9{ \nfont-size: 13px !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9 ,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9:before,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9:after,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9:hover,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9:focus,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9 *,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9 *:before,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9 *:after,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9 *:hover,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd9 *:focus{ \nfont-size: 13px !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48iibgd8 ,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd8:before,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd8:after,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd8 *,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd8 *:before,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd8 *:after{ \ncolor: #490042 !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48iibgd8{ \nfont-family: Georgia, serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48iibgd8:before,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd8:after,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd8:hover,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd8:focus,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd8 *,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd8 *:before,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd8 *:after,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd8 *:hover,\n.ffb-id-48iibgd8 *:focus{ \nfont-family: Georgia, serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48iibq71{ padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 30px;padding-bottom: 30px;padding-left: 30px;}.ffb-id-48iibq75{ padding-bottom: 30px;}.ffb-id-48iibq75 ,.ffb-id-48iibq75:before,.ffb-id-48iibq75:after,.ffb-id-48iibq75 *,.ffb-id-48